 * - Hub: 280px diameter at 60% (mathematically calculated)
 * - Cards: 240px wide, Credit Sculpt at top:0, Capital at bottom-right:0, Properties at bottom-left:0
 * - All SVG icons use hardcoded stroke colors (fixes Astro rendering)
