 * From visual measurement at 55% position:
 * - Credit Sculpt effective bottom: CB = 249px
 * - Bottom cards effective top: BT = 444px
 * - For equal overlap: H = (CB + BT) / 2 = 346.5px = 60%
 * 
 * Verification at 60% (348px center, 140px radius):
 * - Hub top edge: 208px → Credit overlap: 249-208 = 41px
 * - Hub bottom edge: 488px → Bottom overlap: 488-444 = 44px
 * - Equal within margin of error ✓
 * 
 * Responsive Strategy:
 * - Desktop (768px+): Full circular flywheel (680×580px)
 * - Tablet (768-1023px): Scaled to 0.7x
 * - Mobile (<768px): Vertical stack with arrows
 * 
 * Usage:
 * import FlywheelVisual from '@components/FlywheelVisual.astro';
 * <FlywheelVisual />
 */

